<refsection condition="ref.description">
<title>Description</title>

<para>A <tag>union</tag> describes a union in the programming language sense.
Unions represent a collection of items, often of disparate types.</para>

<para>This is one of the few places where DocBook attempts to model as
well as describe. The content model of <tag>union</tag> was designed
to capture a wide range of semantics.</para>

